{
  "texts": [
    "For example, designer A may design a famous sweater S in the physical world, while designer B may digitize this sweater into the Metaverse.",
    "The copyright ownership of sweater S in the Metaverse then becomes controversial.",
    "The definition and protection of copyright for fashion items in the Metaverse is a topic that needs to be fully discussed and constrained.",
    "Legal issues of avatars A digital avatar serves as the vessel of a real-world individual within the Metaverse.",
    "The question of whether identities in the Metaverse should have a one-to-one correspondence with natural persons is a topic worthy of discussion (Yang 2023)."
  ]
}